"A maioria dos casos de uso para essa classe específica é coberta por equivalentes do Jakarta REST, exceto pela obtenção do IP do cliente remoto."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/resteasy.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"RESTEasy comes with a replacement API that you can inject:\n"
"https://docs.jboss.org/resteasy/docs/4.5.6.Final/javadocs/org/jboss/resteasy/spi/HttpRequest.html[`HttpRequest`], which has the methods\n"
"https://docs.jboss.org/resteasy/docs/4.5.6.Final/javadocs/org/jboss/resteasy/spi/HttpRequest.html#getRemoteAddress--[`getRemoteAddress()`]\n"
"and https://docs.jboss.org/resteasy/docs/4.5.6.Final/javadocs/org/jboss/resteasy/spi/HttpRequest.html#getRemoteHost--[`getRemoteHost()`]\n"
"to solve this problem."
msgstr ""
"O RESTEasy vem com uma API de substituição que você pode injetar:\n"
"https://docs.jboss.org/resteasy/docs/4.5.6.Final/javadocs/org/jboss/resteasy/spi/HttpRequest.html[`HttpRequest`], que possui os métodos\n"
"https://docs.jboss.org/resteasy/docs/4.5.6.Final/javadocs/org/jboss/resteasy/spi/HttpRequest.html#getRemoteAddress--[`getRemoteAddress()`]\n"
"e https://docs.jboss.org/resteasy/docs/4.5.6.Final/javadocs/org/jboss/resteasy/spi/HttpRequest.html#getRemoteHost--[`getRemoteHost()`]\n"
"para resolver esse problema."

#. type: Title =
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/resteasy.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
